refentry.refsect1:
&ref.title.attributes;
Attributes for FtpDeployTask
&taskAttributes.table.titlesLine.all;
host
String
The hostname of the remote server.
&attributes.defaultValue.NA;
&attributes.required.yes;
port
Boolean
The port of the remote server.
21
&attributes.required.no;
username
String
The username to use when logging in to the remote server.
&attributes.defaultValue.NA;
&attributes.required.yes;
password
String
The password to use when logging in to the remote server
&attributes.defaultValue.NA;
&attributes.required.yes;
dir
String
Directory on the remote server.
&attributes.defaultValue.NA;
&attributes.required.no;
mode
String
The transfer mode to use, either ascii or binary.
binary
&attributes.required.no;
clearfirst
Boolean
Delete all files in the remote directory before uploading
false
&attributes.required.no;
passive
Boolean
Open connection in passive mode
false
&attributes.required.no;
level
String
Control the level at which the task reports status messages. One of error, warning, info, verbose, debug.
verbose
&attributes.required.no;
